nley@gmail.com Office Hours: Monday through Friday 8:00am to 12:00pm; 2:00pm to 5:00pm Saturday 8:00am to 10:00am; by appointment Foreign Languages Spoken: Chezc Chiropractic College: Palmer College of Chiropractic Graduated: 1989 In Practice Since: 1989 Post Graduate: Certified Chiropractic Extremities Practitioner","location":"Kailua-Kona","rating":5,"lat":19.63581,"lng":-155.980463,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"4b7a1638-a9a4-4410-aead-84b57d65cccb","name":"Jesse Broderson","title":"$undefined","businessName":"$undefined","image":"https://www.malamachiropractic.com/wp-content/uploads/bb-plugin/cache/Chiropractor-Kailua-Kona-HI-Jesse-Broderson-circle.jpg","type":"practitioner","modality":"Chiropractic","modalities":["Chiropractic"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"Chiropractic Care begins with finding a great chiropractor. In Kailua-Kona residents and visitors have a lot of choices- what makes Malama Chiropractic Clinic stand out in our community is that we follow The Golden Rule - we treat our patients how we would want to be treated. To us, this means listening to our patients, finding and treating the real cause of their pain or concern. It’s why all treatments start with a short massage and end with time to lie down and relax. It’s why we have assembled a team of knowledgeable staff and caring Kailua-Kona HI chiropractors to…","location":"Kailua-Kona","rating":5,"lat":0,"lng":0,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"1ca59d25-7e9b-45f9-86cd-3a1b3d4f82eb","name":"Upper Cervical Chiropractic","title":"$undefined","businessName":"Head and Neck Center of Hawai'i LLC","image":"https://hancoh.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/main-logo-1024x211-1.png","type":"practitioner","modality":"Chiropractic","modalities":["Chiropractic"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"We Specialize in Upper Cervical Chiropractic Care for the\nTreatment Headache/Migraine, Neck/Jaw Pain, Concussion\nSymptoms, and More\n\nThis technique, known as Atlas Orthogonal, is a gentle, precise procedure to realign the first cervical vertebrae (atlas).  This techniques has been used to treat patients with migraines (headaches), concussion symptoms, TMJ, and other head and neck related conditions.","location":"Kailua-Kona","rating":5,"lat":19.637333,"lng":-155.98888,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"4b292131-e166-472f-93b2-863e85b5e390","name":"Mauna Lani Chiropractic","title":"$undefined","businessName":"Mauna Lani Chiropractic","image":"http://www.maunalanichiropractic.com/client-portal-api/practice-website-uploads/210758","type":"practitioner","modality":"Chiropractic, Massage","modalities":["Chiropractic","Massage"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"Chiropractic in Kamuela, HI offering Chiropractic services. Paperwork can be filled out online. Schedule an appointment today. ","location":"Waimea","rating":5,"lat":19.941648,"lng":-155.858465,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"aafd38cf-0af7-47f5-943a-f9d5da06baa5","name":"Mikal Barchenger","title":"$undefined","businessName":"$undefined","image":"","type":"practitioner","modality":"Chiropractic","modalities":["Chiropractic"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"","location":"Kailua-Kona","rating":5,"lat":19.641206,"lng":-155.994567,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"5f1f37c9-0e73-42e8-96b4-6d1add49d677","name":"Miranda Chiropractic","title":"$undefined","businessName":"$undefined","image":"","type":"practitioner","modality":"Chiropractic","modaliti